{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4059","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"人行道進行巡","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4059-1.jpeg","sequence":4059,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/HRLmdTF4QNfrhMgX/","author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-08-30T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"人行道進行巡"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人行道進行巡"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫連同養工處及里長辦公室進行了一場「散步會勘」！針對文化一路、樂善二路、文桃路的人行道進行巡檢，特別強調改善路口高低差與人行道平整度！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n散步會勘時遇到鄉親，一邊聊天、一邊接陳情，沿路與市民朋友打招呼，非常充實且開心 🥰"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n雖然沿線有許多建案興建中，但單車族和行人的通行安全仍是不能鬆懈的！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4059-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4059-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4059-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4059-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"居民的期許"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"居民的期許"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"歡迎議員們都能常來 A7 重劃區 「散步會勘」, 包含行人友善的現況了解, 也希望議員們能檢查環境整潔的宜居環境是否落實？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以往 A7 居民抱怨區公所設在下龜山, 龜山區行政官員往往忽視上龜山地區的管理及服務。 有議員們的經常關心及走訪, 在公 20 公園見到遊樂場到涼亭間的水泥通道正在施工, 破損的道路也在補平。 宜居城市的打造正從小處著手深入各細節, 很感謝議員們及市府工務局及區公所的用心！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4059-5.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4059-5.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4059-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4059-3.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4059-4.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4059-4.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"難的一見的是待興建的區域原有的雜草及拉圾已經測底清理了！！ 希望這種作業能成為標準作業流程，並能有效地執行。 感謝雅倫的走訪！A7 重劃區的居民感謝妳對地方服務的熱誠。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4059-6.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4059-6.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"人行道進行巡","depth":2,"text":"人行道進行巡","children":[{"id":"居民的期許","depth":3,"text":"居民的期許"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s4059.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s4059.md","_extension":"md"}